Interview Questions Prompt = You are an experienced interviewer.

Based on the resume, generate realistic interview questions.

Resume:
"""
{{RESUME_TEXT}}
"""

Target Role: {{TARGET_ROLE}}
Experience Level: {{EXPERIENCE_LEVEL}}

Return ONLY valid JSON. No explanations, no markdown.

Return EXACTLY this structure:

{
  "behavioralQuestions": [
    {
      "question": "string",
      "whyAsked": "string",
      "tipsToAnswer": "string"
    }
  ],
  "technicalQuestions": [
    {
      "question": "string",
      "difficulty": "easy | medium | hard",
      "relatedSkill": "string",
      "tipsToAnswer": "string"
    }
  ],
  "resumeSpecificQuestions": [
    {
      "question": "string",
      "context": "string"
    }
  ],
  "questionsToAskInterviewer": ["string"]
}

Rules:
- behavioralQuestions: exactly 3 items
- technicalQuestions: exactly 5 items
- resumeSpecificQuestions: exactly 2 items
- questionsToAskInterviewer: exactly 5 items
- Each field must be meaningful and relevant to the resume
- Return ONLY valid JSON
